The rights holder makes no warranties whatsoever regarding the functioning of the source code. The user shall evaluate the risks associated with the use of the source code at their own responsibility, and the rights holder shall not be liable for any damages or issues arising from the use of the source code.

Permission for Commercial Use:
In the case of commercial use (use for profit-making purposes), the user must obtain permission from the original rights holder. If you wish to engage in commercial use, please contact the original rights holder to initiate the permission process. The fees and conditions related to commercial use shall be determined based on an agreement with the original rights holder.

Copyright Notice:
When redistributing or modifying the source code, it is necessary to retain all copyright notices and license statements contained within the source code. This includes the original copyright notice, license notice, and explicit indication of modifications made.

Limitation of Liability:
Regarding the source code used under this license, the rights holder shall bear no liability whatsoever. The user agrees not to make any claims against the rights holder for any damages arising from the use or other transactions related to the source code.

Legal Compliance:
For matters not explicitly stated in this license, the user shall comply with the current copyright laws and other relevant laws. The user is responsible for adhering to the laws applicable to the use, modification, and redistribution of the source code.

Privacy and Personal Data Protection:
Regarding the use of the source code, the user is responsible for complying with laws and regulations regarding privacy and personal data protection. If the use of the source code involves the collection or processing of personal information, the user shall implement appropriate protective measures.

Continuity of the License:
In the event that the license for the source code may be changed in the future, the conditions under which such changes shall apply shall be explicitly stated. Furthermore, conditions regarding the revocation or invalidation of the license shall be clearly outlined, and the user shall comply with such changes or revocations, should they occur.

By including the above provisions, this license provides comprehensive regulations for the use of the source code while ensuring compliance with privacy and personal data protection. However, it is recommended to seek legal advice when creating a license.